@nluehr is it possible that the update we made to eigen broke the build for cuda 8?

body:
@Pelups the android demo should not need CUDA.
Is it possible during configuration you configured TF to build with CUDA? That would add `--config=cuda` automatically to the build.

@nluehr is it possible that the update we made to eigen broke the build for cuda 8?
